README.md
Midnight Drop Backend
A lightweight, high-performance flash sale reservation service built with Fastify. This backend handles inventory management and ensures users can only reserve a product once during a promotional drop.

Features
Atomic-ready reservation logic: In-memory tracking to handle quick requests.

Duplicate Prevention: Prevents the same userId from making multiple reservations.

CORS Enabled: Ready for integration with your frontend portal.

Configurable: Easily adjust ports, product IDs, and stock levels via .env.

Prerequisites
 (v18 or higher recommended)

npm or yarn

