API Documentation
1. Get Current Stock
Retrieves the current remaining inventory for the product.

URL: /stock

Method: GET

Success Response: ```json
{ "productId": "product_1", "stock": 10 }

2. Reserve Product
Attempts to reserve one unit of the product for a specific user.

URL: /reserve

Method: POST

Body:

Success Response (200):

Error Responses:

400: User ID required / Already purchased

410: Sold out
